Jess!

28:58.120 --> 28:59.360
Apa khabar?

28:59.440 --> 29:01.160
Apa khabar Barbados?

29:02.040 --> 29:04.160
Kami bukan di Barbados, Trevor.

29:04.680 --> 29:06.080
Kami di London.

29:06.160 --> 29:07.000
Oh.

29:07.080 --> 29:10.360
Kami menghabiskan dua hari di Heathrow
menunggu penerbangan kami berlepas,

29:10.440 --> 29:12.400
